      <title>乌克兰称其是波罗的海俄罗斯军舰起火的幕后黑手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/ukraine-says-it-s-behind-blaze-on-russian-warship-in-baltic-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位熟悉此次行动的官员称，乌克兰军事情报部门对波罗的海一艘俄罗斯海军导弹航母的袭击负有责任，这突显了基辅对远离前线的克里姆林宫部队进行打击的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/ukraine-says-it-s-behind-blaze-on-russian-warship-in-baltic-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meloni 团队预计意大利 2024 年经济增长 1%，但债务增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/meloni-team-sees-italy-2024-growth-of-1-but-with-debt-rising</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据政府的最新展望，意大利有望在 2024 年实现超出大多数预测的增长，但其债务负担在未来几年将呈上升趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/meloni-team-sees-italy-2024-growth-of-1-but-with-debt-rising</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:09:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
